	@echo "$(BLUE)⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢈⡏⠀⠀⠀⢠⣼⣿⣿⡿⠘⠛⠛⢓⡄⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢳⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀"
